# Railway Deployment Configuration

# This file helps Railway detect and build your Spring Boot application
# Railway automatically detects Spring Boot projects, but this provides explicit configuration

# Build command (optional - Railway auto-detects Maven)
# Railway will run: mvn clean install -DskipTests

# Start command (optional - Railway auto-detects Spring Boot)
# Railway will run: java -jar target/*.jar

# Make sure to set these environment variables in Railway:
# - SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE=prod
# - DATABASE_URL (automatically set when you add PostgreSQL)
# - cors.allowed.origins=https://your-vercel-app.vercel.app
